data.description: Contemporary home in secluded setting. Bright living room/dining area w/ fireplace. Sliders to upper deck. Kitchen w/ lots of storage & eat-in bar & flows into family room w/ sliders to upper deck. Lower level w/ spacious primary bedroom & private bath w/ sliders to deck. 3 more bedrooms  provide space for guests or office. Each room has serene forest views. Full bath & laundry complete lower level. Outside is a quiet & private forested area. Close to restaurants, shopping, hiking parks, U of O & Lane CC.
